{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1682-11_136"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet sur une Haye d’Epines"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", novembre 1682 [tome 13], p. 136-139."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy un Sonnet que j’ay reçeu sur le sujet de la Haye d’Epines que je proposay il y a quelques mois dans une de mes Lettres. Je n’ay pû vous l’envoyer plutost, à cause d’un grand nombre d’Articles ausquels il m’a falu donner place."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SONNET"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "Sur une Haye d’Epines."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Trop injuste Chasseur, où vous emportez-vous ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Je garantis mon Champ, mes Moutons, & mes Pailles ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si j’ay dans mon Enclos des Perdrix, & des Cailles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Je tâche de les mettre à l’abry de vos coups."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vous, d’un Fer tranchant vous y faites des trous,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous renversez ainsi d’innocentes Murailles,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et venez devorer jusque dans mes entrailles"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce que je sauve bien de la fureur des Loups."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mes branches, il est vray, sont étroitement jointes ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais aux seuls Ravisseurs je présente mes pointes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Lors que pour mes Voisins je n’ay que des bouquets."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Portez, portez ailleurs vos pas, & vostre Chasse,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Et laissez à mon Maistre une petite place"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "A garder sa Maison, ses Vergers, ses Guérets."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy que rien ne paroisse plus stérile que les Epines, il faut demeurer d’accord que ce Sonnet ne manque pas de beautez. Cela fait voir qu’il n’y a point de matieres épineuses pour les Personnes d’esprit. Ceux qui ont du talent pour la Poësie, peuvent le faire paroître sur un Torrent. C’est le sujet qu’on leur propose pour travailler."}]}]}